document: Student Handbook: Comprehensive guide to student resources, rules, and procedures.
Exam Policy: Policies for scheduling, grading, and retakes during exam periods.
Academic Integrity: Standards for honest work, citation, and misconduct handling.
Thesis Guidelines: Formatting rules, submission process, and evaluation criteria.
Scholarship Info: Eligibility, application timelines, and required documentation.
Course Catalog: List of all courses, prerequisites, and credit details.
Internship Guide: How to apply, find placements, and report internship progress.
Exam Schedule: Dates, times, rooms, and proctoring guidance for exams.
Graduation Checklist: Steps to finalize studies and prepare for commencement.
Library Policy: Borrowing limits, fines, and digital archive usage policies.
